review.body: Thanks for your contribution. This looks very good, indeed. Some questions to the code separately asked: Please comment. Then, there's reference to a ready-made docker image: For this to be generated, there needs to be code in CCI (.circleci/config.config.yml): Would you be able to add such code? If you're not familiar with CCI, I'll try to do it in a follow-up PR, but maybe you want to give it a try.
